title: recipes_Orange_Johnny_Cake
text:
Title: Orange Johnny Cake.
.
Description: Corn muffin mix is flavored with grated orange zest and baked..
.
Ingredients:.
- 1 (8.5 ounce) package dry corn muffin mix.
- 1 egg, beaten.
- 0.33300000429153 cup milk.
- 3 tablespoons grated orange zest.
.
Instructions:.
- Preheat oven to 400 degrees F (200 degrees C). Lightly grease an 8x8 inch baking pan..
- In a large bowl, stir together muffin mix, egg, milk and orange zest. Pour batter into prepared pan..
- Bake in preheated oven for 20 to 25 minutes, until golden brown..
.
